---
title: Honey Mustard Beef Rissoles with Roasted Veggies & Creamy Pesto
description: How do you improve on the humble rissole? Add honey for sweetness and some mustard for a touch of tanginess then serve your new creations with a roasted veggie salad and oodles of creamy pesto. Suddenly, the classic dish goes from simple to stunning!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bc521cb30006c33c42efb23-84f81317.jpg
